text:
Catelynn Lowell's Family

Catelynn Lowell and Tyler Baltierra have been together since they were young teens, and they tied the knot in 2015. They put their first daughter, Carly, up for adoption in 2009, and had a second daughter, Novalee, in 2015. Their family tree is probably the most straight-forward one in the whole Teen Mom franchise. Well, except for that whole Catelynn's-mom-married-Tyler's-dad thing, making them step-siblings. The couple also has legal custody of Catelynn's younger sister Sarah, who's now an adult. Rumor had it they were trying for more children, but after suffering from a miscarriage just a few months ago, they may have put those plans on pause.
